  • AI Voice Assistant for Smart Control Activate Google Assistant or Siri directly from your Bluetooth calling smartwatch. Use voice commands to check the weather, set alarms, control music, or get real-time updates all hands-free

  • 110+ Sports Modes & Accurate Fitness Tracking Get the best out of your workouts with 110+ sports modes, including running, walking, cycling, yoga, football, and more.   • IP67 Waterproof Smartwatch for Active Lifestyles Built to endure splashes, sweat, and dust, this IP67-rated smartwatch is perfect for workouts, outdoor sports, and all-day wear, ensuring durability in every situation
